            <h1>Covid-19 Metrics Endpoint</h1>
            <p>This endpoint allows access to the daily metrics for the number of Covid-19 cases in the United States</p>
        <h3>How to use:</h3>
        <p>All you have to do to use this API is to navigate to this webpage's url and add the following parameters to the url:</p>
        
        <ol>
            <li>Date: yyyy-m-d Based on the UTC standards (OPTIONAL)</li>
        </ol>

        <p>If you navigate to the covid/metrics endpoint without any paramenters it will return all of the Covid-19 reported cases for all dates</p>
        <h3>Example:</h3>
        <p>If I wanted to get all metrics for April 6th, 2020, I would use the following url:</p>
        <p>http://metricsapi-env.eba-3e3yt2se.us-west-1.elasticbeanstalk.com/covid/metrics?date=2020-3-6</p>
